 class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係個人問題姐，唔好懶部車"},{"pid":"d9e12272dfc7f7b9500d201f0ed594391b2f213f","tid":266822,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會渣壞手勢<br />\n建議舞掂頭轆車先好玩四䡱</blockquote><br />\n有電子輔助既車都會揸壞手勢<br />\nEven brake"},{"pid":"b038a13aa50d02d6e12f4e98409683b2fa2a7feb","tid":266822,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會渣壞手勢<br />\n建議舞掂頭轆車先好玩四䡱</blockquote><br />\n請問Ching 有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係個人問題姐，唔好懶部車</blockquote><br />\n我唔係話四䡱車唔好<br />\n四䡱好安全,stability好好<br />\n四䡱車同頭轆車掟彎<br />\n四䡱穩定好多<br />\n就係因為你一開始渣慣四䡱<br />\n之後你掟果d彎就會愈黎愈快<br />\n如果你之後渣番頭轆就唔慣<br />\n利申：之前賣左部sti之後渣ae110<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然呢d係個人問題<br />\n但我認為新手應該渣下頭轆車先<br />\n感受下個handling先再考慮玩四䡱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95edc8745d2e5e17d98d57b97924adbbb38d4d25","tid":266822,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會渣壞手勢<br />\n建議舞掂頭轆車先好玩四䡱</blockquote><br />\n請問Ching 有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係個人問題姐，唔好懶部車</blockquote><br />\n我唔係話四䡱車唔好<br />\n四䡱好安全,stability好好<br />\n四䡱車同頭轆車掟彎<br />\n四䡱穩定好多<br />\n就係因為你一開始渣慣四䡱<br />\n之後你掟果d彎就會愈黎愈快<br />\n如果你之後渣番頭轆就唔慣<br />\n利申：之前賣左部sti之後渣ae110<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然呢d係個人問題<br />\n但我認為新手應該渣下頭轆車先<br />\n感受下個handling先再考慮玩四䡱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsti 同ae110點比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e49cbdd7c471bab4067502eea82afacc8ce3e3","tid":266822,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會渣壞手勢<br />\n建議舞掂頭轆車先好玩四䡱</blockquote><br />\n請問Ching 有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係個人問題姐，唔好懶部車</blockquote><br />\n我唔係話四䡱車唔好<br />\n四䡱好安全,stability好好<br />\n四䡱車同頭轆車掟彎<br />\n四䡱穩定好多<br />\n就係因為你一開始渣慣四䡱<br />\n之後你掟果d彎就會愈黎愈快<br />\n如果你之後渣番頭轆就唔慣<br />\n利申：之前賣左部sti之後渣ae110<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然呢d係個人問題<br />\n但我認為新手應該渣下頭轆車先<br />\n感受下個handling先再考慮玩四䡱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsti 同ae110點比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI mean渣番頭轆車好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個例子係差左d既sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cfc7cc2e1b9a7fc91f3c0ab7b26a43e465250e","tid":266822,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"留名，好想坐下掃把妹手車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46946d693c19524c88084095b988f544033f1083","tid":266822,"uid":69626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:01:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名，好想坐下掃把妹手車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，剩係佢坐過我車，我冇坐過佢車，唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c819af368ee3618d8d8615df1ebe79b8ba471680","tid":266822,"uid":41102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:24:41.000Z","msg":"答單問下<br />\nwrx gh8<br />\nlegacy bl5<br />\n2部都08年車 大家揀邊部？<br />\n同埋油錢維修既價如何<br />\n有咩要留意？<br />\n想入手掃把 但驚養唔掂"},{"pid":"412167552f3130ce253ca035e02159cb169c7b0d","tid":266822,"uid":59046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T23:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>答單問下<br />\nwrx gh8<br />\nlegacy bl5<br />\n2部都08年車 大家揀邊部？<br />\n同埋油錢維修既價如何<br />\n有咩要留意？<br />\n想入手掃把 但驚養唔掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我揀bl5  <br />\n設備, spec bl5  &gt; gh8<br />\n如果係aim bl5 spec b (6mt) 就更加係bl5<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n維修 bl5 = gh8<br />\n個軚揼一定會壞<br />\n壞左就整3千 (2手rebuild 揼價錢)<br />\n<br />\n另外08年車有啲parts 都夠鐘換 <br />\ne.g. cam帶 brake rotor <br />\n套避震彈弓<br />\n<br />\n你預買架bl5 要俾多10k 執一執<br />\n之後就爽到4-5年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n油錢方面<br />\n同一種使用習慣<br />\n部3.5 na 7人車 行緊17l/100km<br />\n而部bl5 2.0turbo 行緊13l/100km"},{"pid":"d094d907cbaab17727720f036cdbc57beab89d32","tid":266822,"uid":41102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>答單問下<br />\nwrx gh8<br />\nlegacy bl5<br />\n2部都08年車 大家揀邊部？<br />\n同埋油錢維修既價如何<br />\n有咩要留意？<br />\n想入手掃把 但驚養唔掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我揀bl5  <br />\n設備, spec bl5  &gt; gh8<br />\n如果係aim bl5 spec b (6mt) 就更加係bl5<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n維修 bl5 = gh8<br />\n個軚揼一定會壞<br />\n壞左就整3千 (2手rebuild 揼價錢)<br />\n<br />\n另外08年車有啲parts 都夠鐘換 <br />\ne.g. cam帶 brake rotor <br />\n套避震彈弓<br />\n<br />\n你預買架bl5 要俾多10k 執一執<br />\n之後就爽到4-5年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n油錢方面<br />\n同一種使用習慣<br />\n部3.5 na 7人車 行緊17l/100km<br />\n而部bl5 2.0turbo 行緊13l/100km</blockquote><br />\n13L係有無得閒踩2腳？<br />\n其實油錢都唔平....<br />\n我個range係1.3-1.7<br />\n姐係平時得閒爽2腳都係1.7左右<br />\n如果正常腳都1.6就有DD甘"},{"pid":"cdd87011e984e6584bbce03f344b6d94599df133","tid":266822,"uid":47145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸R2囉，都係掃把佬啫</blockquote><br />\n揸緊R1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bf9cbd200482e347d50b83ac9acb13e205ad11","tid":266822,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"棍仔? 練車真係一流."}]}